query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mi_idx t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc mi_idx t mi) */ select count(*)
from title AS t
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.kind_id = 1 AND mi_idx.info_type_id = 101
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_type_id = 2
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 16;
